# Marker written by e2e globalSetup recording the build inputs the running
# test-emulator image was built from (drives the stale-image rebuild check).
docker/test-emulators/.image-build-hash

# Serena MCP (oraios/serena) — local semantic-code-search state, entirely
# machine-specific and regenerable via `serena project index`. Nothing under
# .serena/ belongs in git: cache/ is the LSP symbol index, logs/ is noise, and
# project.yml is regenerated on activation.
#
# NOTE: project.yml's defaults are WRONG for this repo and must be re-applied
# after any regeneration — `languages: [typescript]` (Serena's Svelte LSP gives
# unreliable references, so semantic tools are TS-only here) and
# `ignored_paths: [".claude/**"]` (otherwise it indexes the 18 duplicate
# checkouts under .claude/worktrees/ despite them being gitignored: 17,734 files
# and ~59 min, versus ~790 files in ~3 min when scoped correctly).
.serena/
